{"tid":454341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞漢被劫3千元金鏈 警追緝同鄉","createTime":"2017-11-01T04:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T05:26:29.000Z","uid":51904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"68320e578e1126a31571a99a10307dc89cce201e","tid":454341,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"昨午5時許，油麻地吳松街93號一單位，一名28歲南亞漢，被同鄉友人以刀指嚇，劫去一條金鏈，約值3千元。警員經初步調查後，案件暫列行劫，交油尖警區刑事調查第七隊跟進，追緝該名約1.7米高，約25至30歲，中等身材，案發時身穿黑色上衣及黑色長褲南亞男子。"},{"pid":"50de821abb4fcc21f196164ecc229005c8b33888","tid":454341,"uid":31408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"蝻連自己友都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c2a4a23e14eb2375ce16620de66e1e0ae67fc7","tid":454341,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:56:47.000Z","msg":"好危險，男人都會比人搶"},{"pid":"540c2cc42cd467f5c0950e7ab3ef891c3a60560e","tid":454341,"uid":85557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://7.share.photo.xuite.net/hungpont/17ee985/12583981/631213144_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F7.share.photo.xuite.net%2Fhungpont%2F17ee985%2F12583981%2F631213144_m.jpg&h=ef533dc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5db60cfae38a4b39110af2693c7008886c209282","tid":454341,"uid":62532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:21:14.000Z","msg":"見到搶同鄉即刻安心左<br />\n原來佢地都一視同人"},{"pid":"ec56096dc1f263b626a78d2e10598d188e9d6437","tid":454341,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"蝻 On 蝻 action"}]}